reviewText:
Nice game.
Great art direction;
Great historic research and storytelling;
Beautiful artwork and effects;
Amazing soundtrack and very good voice acting.
Smooth gameplay;
Fight ancient deities, monsters and solve puzzles;
Relatively non linear game, freedom to break rules (robery, murder);
MULTIPLAYER ARENA INCREDIBLY FUN - You must play it, there is a free download!

Cons:
The campaign is a little bit slow and tiresome.
I would appreciate a bit of character customization.
Wait for a sale, the price is a bit overestimate.

P.S.: The devs should do a egyptian themed game!

